This package bundles tokenizer assets derived from official Hugging Face repositories under the zai-org organization:
- zai-org/GLM-4.7 tokenizer.json
- zai-org/GLM-5 tokenizer.json

The bundled snapshots currently cover these official model groups:
- GLM-4.5 / GLM-4.5-Base / GLM-4.5-Air / GLM-4.5-Air-Base / GLM-4.6 / GLM-4.7
- GLM-4.7-Flash / GLM-5

